type.description: You can change the type of the divider by setting the type prop to solid, dotted or dashed. Defaults to solid.
type.description_zh: You can change the type of the divider by setting the type prop to solid, dotted or dashed. Defaults to solid.

:avatar.description: Use the avatar prop as an object and configure it with any of its props.
:avatar.description_zh: Use the avatar prop as an object and configure it with any of its props.

orientation.description: You can change the orientation of the divider by setting the orientation prop to horizontal or vertical. Defaults to horizontal.
orientation.description_zh: You can change the orientation of the divider by setting the orientation prop to horizontal or vertical. Defaults to horizontal.
